{
  "texts": [
    "Average ratings for each dimension (empathy, reliability, comprehensibility, willingness to follow the advice) and author label (Human, AI, Human + AI).",
    "Samples for each author label condition were independent from each other, but each participant provided ratings for all dimensions.",
    "Ratings are aggregated across all four scenarios and responses are scaled from 1 to 5, with higher values indicating stronger expressions of the respective dimension.",
    "Error bars show standard errors of the individual means.",
    "Our findings may be based on a stronger association of the \"human physician\" label with a mutual demonstration of care and respect, which are vital factors for successful patientphysician interactions (14)."
  ]
}